## Releasing

To release a new version:
- update the version number in the CHANGELOG and Makefile
- cat the new version into gzap/apworld/uzdoom/VERSION
  (autodetection will instead detect it as <prevision version>-<build number>-<commit>,
  since we haven't tagged yet)
- rm -rf release/apworlds/zdoom_* gzap/apworld/zdoom_* && touch docs/apworld-generator.sh && make
  (this generates binaries with the right version number baked in)
- copy the apworld-generator.html to apworld-generator-<version>.html and update the links therein
- commit
- tag and push the commit
- cut the release on github using the just-generated pk3 and apworld as the binaries

